  "detailed_description": "666 Second Rule an Unholy Adventure<br><br>666 Second Rule is a short action game where you take the role of a messed-up parent pretending to care about your child and using the dark forces on your  journey. The baby is on the dirty-dirty ground. You know what can happen!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/d94d65514d915cf231812b3a96cb1793.poster.avif?t=1708423229\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/d94d65514d915cf231812b3a96cb1793.webm?t=1708423229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/d94d65514d915cf231812b3a96cb1793.mp4?t=1708423229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐜 Slay Swarms of Insects 🐜</h2><br>Arm yourself with swift reflexes and battle through hordes of pesky insects! With each foe vanquished, collect their legs as dark currency to unlock the secrets of the shadow realm.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/305ae1f4939b8d4f51f11a1bbfc81448.poster.avif?t=1708423229\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/305ae1f4939b8d4f51f11a1bbfc81448.webm?t=1708423229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/305ae1f4939b8d4f51f11a1bbfc81448.mp4?t=1708423229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👟 Upgrade Your Arsenal 👟</h2><br>Experience the thrill of wielding new, stronger slippers as you progress through the twisted narrative. Crush your enemies with enhanced power and show no mercy to those who stand in your way!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/635078158cfd517f6c1d01dc8f2eb19e.poster.avif?t=1708423229\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/635078158cfd517f6c1d01dc8f2eb19e.webm?t=1708423229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/635078158cfd517f6c1d01dc8f2eb19e.mp4?t=1708423229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌟 Harness Sinister Powers 🌟</h2><br>Delve deeper into the occult and harness the might of pentagrams and other dark powers. Unleash devastating spells and bend the forces of nature to your will!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/1736823782a52db3c8e389b3f50b3a88.poster.avif?t=1708423229\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/1736823782a52db3c8e389b3f50b3a88.webm?t=1708423229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540110/extras/1736823782a52db3c8e389b3f50b3a88.mp4?t=1708423229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >❌ Desperate Times, Desperate Measures ❌</h2><br>The child's life hangs in the balance, but beware - the path to redemption is riddled with malevolence. Can you navigate through the twisted choices and save the cute innocent baby from the clutches of the darkness?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 Experience 666 Second Rule Now! 🎮</h2><br>Embark on this gripping action-packed journey, fraught with sinister powers and a heart-stopping quest to rescue the child from a fate worse than death!<br><br>🔥 WISHLIST NOW 🔥",
